<font face="Arial" size="2">We are excited to share with you the following investment and fundraising updates from <b>Brookfield Fairfield U.S. Multifamily Value Add Fund III ("VAMF III" or the "Main Fund")</b>, a private closed-end vehicle established by the Sponsors<sup>1</sup> to acquire and develop value-add multifamily assets throughout the U.S.:&nbsp;</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
</p>
<ul>	<li style="font-size: 13px;"><font size="2">VAMF III has closed $456 million towards its $850 million target raise<span style="font-family: Arial;"> to-date, of which, $330 million is committed by the Sponsors;<sup>2</sup><br />&nbsp;</span></font></li>	<li><font size="2" style="font-size: 13px;">VAMF III has committed $357 million to-date, or ~42% of its target fund size to twelve closed and pipeline investments</font><font style="font-size: 10.8333px;"><sup>3</sup></font><font size="2" style="font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;in geographically diverse locations in the U.S. with $1 billion of total costs;<sup>4<br />&nbsp;</sup></font></li>	<li style="font-size: 13px;"><font size="2">We recently launched the <b class="">
<g class="gr_ gr_49 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" id="49" data-gr-id="49">iCapital</g></b><span style="font-family: Arial;"><b>-Brookfield Fairfield VAMF III Access Fund, L.P. (the &quot;Access Fund&quot;)</b>, which will substantially invest all of its assets in the Main Fund. The Access Fund provides an additional opportunity for our private wealth clients to access the Main Fund at a minimum investment size of $250,000.<sup>5</sup></span></font></li>
</ul>
<p style="font-size: 13px;">
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial;">For additional details on the terms and conditions of the Access Fund, please refer to the <a href="http://cl.S7.exct.net/?qs=e20df025c5da26b2d6b9ab78eea47cba0f505879447069be3725b6cfadd356403f13514094a4b457693347d13296830157ba89228ec70a8f" title="fact sheet"  >fact sheet</a>.</span></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
</p>
