<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><font face="Arial"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Brookfield Fairfield U.S. Multifamily Value Add Fund III&nbsp;</b></font></font></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><font face="Arial"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font></font></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><font face="Arial"><font face="Arial" size="2" style="font-size: 13px;">We have established VAMF III, a private vehicle to acquire and develop value-add multifamily assets throughout the U.S. and are seeking $850 million in capital commitments.</font><font face="Arial" size="2" style="font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;VAMF III targets a gross IRR of 14-16% (net 12-13%) and a gross investment multiple of 1.8x or greater (1.6x net), with a net cash-on-cash return of 4-6%.<sup>6</sup></font></font></font></p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><font face="Arial"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font></font></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><font face="Arial"><font face="Arial" size="2">Key features of VAMF III include:</font></font></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
</p>
<ul style="font-size: 13px;">	<li><font size="2"><b>Strong Sponsorship. </b>VAMF III will be managed by Fairfield, a multifamily operator, <g class="gr_ gr_50 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep" id="50" data-gr-id="50">developer</g><span style="font-family: Arial;"> and owner </span><g class="gr_ gr_41 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar multiReplace" id="41" data-gr-id="41">with</g><span style="font-family: Arial;"> a vertically integrated platform that performs all functions of the asset life cycle. Fairfield has an operating history of over 20 years and experience in more than 40 geographically diverse markets throughout the U.S., giving it real-time, local market intelligence and insight.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</span>
</font></li>	<li><font size="2"><b>Sourcing. </b>As one of the largest and most active asset managers in the real estate sector globally, we bring great insight into the global capital markets, as well as a strong balance sheet that is expected to allow us to make a significant commitment to VAMF III. VAMF III will leverage Fairfield's extensive in-house capabilities to source attractive investment opportunities and successfully execute value creation initiatives.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</font></li>	<li><font size="2"><b>Established, Long-Term Track Record. </b>Fairfield has an established track record of investing in and managing value-add properties as well as in developing new multifamily
<span style="font-family: Arial;"> projects. Predecessor funds, VAMF I and VAMF II, are currently exceeding initial targets.<sup>7<br />&nbsp;</sup></span></font></li>	<li><font size="2"><b>Compelling Market Opportunity. </b>VAMF III will seek to capitalize on market conditions that we believe will be favorable for multifamily<span style="font-family: Arial;"> investing, including strong demand for rental housing driven by demographic shifts and limited new supply of multifamily inventory.<br />&nbsp;</span></font></li>	<li><font size="2"><b>Seasoned Team of Investment Professionals. </b>The Fund's investment and asset management team <g class="gr_ gr_46 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar multiReplace" id="46" data-gr-id="46">is
</g> comprised of Fairfield professionals with an average of 23 years of experience in multifamily investing. The Fund's investment committee includes our Senior Managing Partners and senior Fairfield professionals who have an average of over 30 years of experience.</font></li>
</ul>
